title: PUPA
body:
If maggots were swapped for horseflies, what would you do with the maggots?

Recommended pre-requisite for reading: Horsefly proposal.

https://vote.rottenswap.org/#/rot/proposal/QmZaR61wWqxhvsEmB5972USMxzamhZZncL4vqo5fPm8HMd
choices: Give x% to MAGGOT/ROT pool holders, x% per day via fly swatter.
Give x% to HORSEFLY/MAGGOT pool holders, x% per day via fly swatter.
